# 🚀 FIX — EXACT COMMANDS (copy-paste)

## 🔥 STEP 1 — FIX `machine-api` webhook

Run:

```bash
oc patch mutatingwebhookconfiguration machine-api \
--type='json' \
-p='[
{"op":"replace","path":"/webhooks/0/rules/0/apiVersions","value":["v1"]},
{"op":"replace","path":"/webhooks/1/rules/0/apiVersions","value":["v1"]}
]'
```

